---
title: Gochujang Pulled Pork Hungry Vampire Bao with Thai Style Spiced Chips, Pickled Cucumber and Sriracha Slaw
description: Serve up a fright this Halloween with our fiendishly flavoursome recipes. Stuffed full of flavour, these Gochujang Pulled Pork Hungry Vampire Bao are a fusion favourite. Complimented by two delicious sides, these brilliant bao are destined to be a treat for your table.
